Can you remember any of the rules and regulations there,

00:31:36.520 --> 00:31:38.520
were there...

00:31:38.520 --> 00:31:40.520
Did you feel there were rules and regulations or...?

00:31:40.520 --> 00:31:42.520
Well, you weren't allowed to be late,

00:31:42.520 --> 00:31:44.520
you had to be clocking in.

00:31:46.520 --> 00:31:48.520
But there was no really rules,

00:31:48.520 --> 00:31:50.520
I mean, you just had to be... couldn't be late.

00:31:50.520 --> 00:31:53.520
I mean, you had to have a good excuse for not being in work.

00:31:54.520 --> 00:31:58.520
But apart from that, there was no really rules,

00:31:58.520 --> 00:32:01.520
because everything was fine, you know what I mean?

00:32:01.520 --> 00:32:03.520
You had a good supervisor.

00:32:06.520 --> 00:32:08.520
Great.

00:32:08.520 --> 00:32:11.520
Were you ever made aware of kind of health and safety issues

00:32:11.520 --> 00:32:14.520
and stuff like that, or, you know, told to be careful?

00:32:14.520 --> 00:32:17.520
No, there was no health and safety.

00:32:17.520 --> 00:32:19.520
The only thing issue was, as I told you,

00:32:19.520 --> 00:32:21.520
with the temperature with the union, that's the only thing.

00:32:21.520 --> 00:32:23.520
There was no health and safety then.

00:32:25.520 --> 00:32:28.520
And how was the factory heated?

00:32:29.520 --> 00:32:31.520
Unlit, do you remember?

00:32:32.520 --> 00:32:35.520
I can't remember the heating, but as I said,

00:32:35.520 --> 00:32:39.520
it wasn't really cold, but then when we had the bitter cold weather,

00:32:39.520 --> 00:32:41.520
it would be cold, because it was a big...

00:32:41.520 --> 00:32:43.520
How can I explain?

00:32:43.520 --> 00:32:46.520
You know, like the two Asdas, these buildings, what they're called now.

00:32:47.520 --> 00:32:49.520
I can't think of the word now.

00:32:49.520 --> 00:32:50.520
The what buildings?

00:32:50.520 --> 00:32:52.520
You know, like Asdas, like they build them, these pre...

00:32:52.520 --> 00:32:54.520
What they're called? I can't think of the word.

00:32:54.520 --> 00:32:56.520
Pre-fabricated things.

00:32:56.520 --> 00:32:58.520
Yeah, you see, that's not the word.

00:32:58.520 --> 00:33:00.520
It was a great big factory, I mean...

00:33:00.520 --> 00:33:02.520
I can't even remember.

00:33:02.520 --> 00:33:04.520
What about the heat?

00:33:04.520 --> 00:33:07.520
All I remember, we were told this time, because it was cold,

