if it was below 40, we weren't allowed to work.

00:33:10.520 --> 00:33:13.520
But I can't remember what heating was in there.

00:33:13.520 --> 00:33:15.520
I think they had the big long lights, you know.

00:33:15.520 --> 00:33:17.520
Because of the sewing, you'd have to have bright lights,

00:33:17.520 --> 00:33:19.520
because of the sewing.

00:33:19.520 --> 00:33:21.520
So like strip lighting?

00:33:21.520 --> 00:33:23.520
Yes, yes.

00:33:27.520 --> 00:33:29.520
Were you really, really worried about the heat?

00:33:29.520 --> 00:33:32.520
Were you allowed to kind of chat while you were working?

00:33:32.520 --> 00:33:34.520
Yes, you could chat and sing.

00:33:34.520 --> 00:33:37.520
Yeah, that's what I said, it was relaxed, it was really nice.

00:33:37.520 --> 00:33:39.520
And do you remember what you talked about?

00:33:39.520 --> 00:33:41.520
Oh, probably boyfriends and what we...

00:33:41.520 --> 00:33:44.520
You know, youth club and different things.

00:33:44.520 --> 00:33:47.520
You know, and music, we talk about the music, like I said,

00:33:47.520 --> 00:33:51.520
there'd be certain records we'd like, and we'd talk about that, you know.

00:33:52.520 --> 00:33:54.520
Things haven't changed that much then?

00:33:54.520 --> 00:33:56.520
No, it hasn't, no.

00:33:56.520 --> 00:33:59.520
Were you allowed to smoke while you were working?

00:33:59.520 --> 00:34:01.520
No, I don't think, no.

00:34:01.520 --> 00:34:04.520
They could smoke, but not in the factory.

00:34:04.520 --> 00:34:08.520
They could, because obviously, they could smoke in the canteen,

00:34:08.520 --> 00:34:11.520
because I never smoked, so it didn't appeal to me.

00:34:11.520 --> 00:34:13.520
But they couldn't smoke in the factory,

00:34:13.520 --> 00:34:16.520
but I think they could smoke in the canteen, you know.

00:34:17.520 --> 00:34:25.520
Did you suffer any kind of long-term health issues from working then?

00:34:25.520 --> 00:34:27.520
No, nothing at all.

00:34:31.520 --> 00:34:35.520
How did the women treat their fellow male workers?

00:34:35.520 --> 00:34:39.520
Fine, they used to laugh about and joke with them, they were fine.

00:34:41.520 --> 00:34:43.520
Okay, okay.

00:34:45.520 --> 00:34:52.520
Was your husband supportive of you working? Did he mind? Did he want you to work?

00:34:52.520 --> 00:34:56.520
Well, in them days, he did. He just automatically worked, didn't he?

00:34:56.520 --> 00:34:58.520
He didn't even think about it.

00:34:58.520 --> 00:35:02.520
I mean, once you've had your children, then you never worked,

00:35:02.520 --> 00:35:04.520
