00:35:09.520 --> 00:35:12.520
because they're missing the bond with their children.

00:35:12.520 --> 00:35:16.520
I really don't like that. I really think it's hard.

00:35:18.520 --> 00:35:20.520
Yeah, yeah.

00:35:20.520 --> 00:35:23.520
How many days did you work? Did you work weekends?

00:35:23.520 --> 00:35:28.520
