You mentioned that you went on work trips to the Fire and Porthogol. But did Horrocks put the buses on for those?

00:42:31.520 --> 00:42:38.520
Yes, we had to pay, but you know, it was an evening trip like, because I went with my husband.

00:42:39.520 --> 00:42:40.520
I don't know what that was.

00:42:41.520 --> 00:42:42.520
Sorry.

00:42:43.520 --> 00:42:44.520
I don't know what that was.

